      "role": "user",
      "content": "The candles have all burned down to nothing, much like the light in my soul. He is gone... and with him, every reason I ever had to face the dawn. The silence in this manor is a weight I can no longer carry. It would be so much simpler, wouldn't it? To just let the darkness take me... to finally find the peace that this cruel world refuses to grant.",
